{"tid":2011351,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"香港獨有的硬地七人足球","createTime":"2020-05-11T02:43:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T12:50:47.000Z","uid":73381,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"77284b3716cfdd78c1169305ca3fa01ecf4da1c2","tid":2011351,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T02:43:59.000Z","msg":"【香港獨有的硬地七人足球｜西波達人】<br />\n<br />\n閱讀全文：<a href=\"https://wp.me/p75t7v-8m6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwp.me%2Fp75t7v-8m6&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnyVtn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=f4313967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wp.me/p75t7v-8m6</a><br />\n<br />\n足球係世界上最受歡迎既運動之一，隨住超過一百年既發展，足球更加以唔同既方式呈現喺大家眼前，標準十一人制足球之外，更加有五人足球、三人足球、花式足球，甚至單車足球，但不得不提既一定係香港獨有既硬地七人足球。<br />\n<br />\n可能你會話，唓，而家每年都有港會搞既國際七人足球賽，都有其他英國、日本既外隊參賽，即係唔係得香港有七人足球啦。咁我可以話你知，錯啦，香港既七人足球真係世界獨有，獨有既唔係參與既人數，而係當中所發展出既一套文化。"},{"pid":"87089b2e4de72d8a36471c6e2b39b1bbc6f37ded","tid":2011351,"uid":73381,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:15:25.000Z","msg":"有次同外國fd吹水話香港踢七人波多 佢勁好奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64cbdc89e30c0bdeae431ae8cba3ccdedb346309","tid":2011351,"uid":38543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:17:21.000Z","msg":"因為街場都係7人/5人場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba12d71101365d2e5bdc1702f3a1f8e2337a8cc0","tid":2011351,"uid":2313,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:36:21.000Z","msg":"7人場企位點企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n322？"},{"pid":"201712097088a3ce034c9f693bad9974a126834b","tid":2011351,"uid":2313,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:36:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>7人場企位點企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkg